<plot>Four members of the Dancing Rabbit Eco-Village, an intentional community in Missouri, express their motivation for living communally and the importance of developing sustainable lifestyles. The film provides an in depth look into the community as it seeks to understand the spirit of its members and the radical steps they've taken to live sustainably.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?339270</url></doc>
